---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout current="about" title="About — maxbabic.dev">
  <section class="about">
    <div class="section-head">
      <h2 class="section-title">About</h2>
      <span class="section-num">/ 03</span>
    </div>

    <div class="about-content">
      <p>
        Hi, I'm Max — a student at VŠB-TUO in Ostrava, currently finishing my
        bachelor's degree at the Faculty of Electrical Engineering and Computer
        Science.
      </p>

      <p>
        My focus is mostly on networking, embedded systems, and anything
        radio-related. I just defended a thesis on a 2.4 GHz LoRaWAN sensor
        node, which involved more RF debugging than I'd care to admit.
      </p>

      <h2>What I'm into</h2>

      <p>
        Self-hosting and home labs (my server is named <em>ferda</em> and runs
        Jellyfin, Immich, Seafile, and a few other things behind Cloudflare
        tunnels). Linux on the desktop. Older European executive cars — I
        drive a 2009 Seat Exeo 1.8T and find it unreasonably charming.
      </p>

      <h2>Currently</h2>

      <p>
        Wrapping up coursework, writing the occasional blog post, and figuring
        out what comes next.
      </p>

      <h2>Reach me</h2>

      <p>
        Email is the most reliable way — <a href="mailto:maxmilian.babic@email.cz">maxmilian.babic@email.cz</a>.
        Code lives on <a href="https://github.com/diamondminer857" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
